      "eyebrow": "",
      "headline": "ABOUT ME",
      "text": "Hi, my name is Arthur, and I started editing videos 5 years ago. At first, I just wanted to take inspiration from the editing style of creators I followed, but I quickly realized I had found something bigger. I started editing for fun, then for family and friends, until I made a decision: to take editing seriously as a career. Since then, I have studied the field every day, which led me to master techniques for different formats and platforms. Today, I am a creative and versatile editor who does not just execute, but thinks through every video with intention, from the first cut to the final delivery.",
